transforms.result: export default "@charset \"UTF-8\";@font-face{font-family:Pretendard;font-weight:400;src:url(/fonts/pretendard/Pretendard-Regular.woff2) format(\"woff2\")}@font-face{font-family:Pretendard;font-weight:500;src:url(/fonts/pretendard/Pretendard-Medium.woff2) format(\"woff2\")}@font-face{font-family:Pretendard;font-weight:600;src:url(/fonts/pretendard/Pretendard-SemiBold.woff2) format(\"woff2\")}@font-face{font-family:Pretendard;font-weight:700;src:url(/fonts/pretendard/Pretendard-Bold.woff2) format(\"woff2\")}body,html{font-family:Pretendard,Apple SD Gothic Neo,nanumgothic,나눔고딕,arial,sans-serif}*{box-sizing:border-box}a{color:inherit;text-decoration:none}img{height:auto;width:100%}.c-modal{--outerMargin:50px;height:100%;left:0;position:fixed;top:0;width:100%;z-index:9999}.c-modal__inner{background:#fff;border-radius:8px;left:50%;max-height:calc(100vh - var(--outerMargin)*2);position:absolute;top:50%;transform:translate(-50%,-50%);width:calc(100vw - var(--outerMargin)*2)}.c-modal__mid{max-height:calc(100vh - var(--outerMargin)*2 - var(--topHeight) - var(--botHeight));overflow:auto;padding-left:40px;padding-right:40px}.c-modal__bot{padding:20px 40px 36px;text-align:right}.c-modal__title{font-size:20px;font-weight:700;line-height:1.4;padding:36px 90px 24px 40px}.c-modal__close{background-color:transparent;color:#e32924;font-size:24px;padding:7px;position:absolute;right:35px;top:30px}.c-modal__confirm-btn{min-width:124px}:global(.c-modal__inner){max-width:600px}"
